A pipeline belonging to the Nigerian National Petroleum Company (NNPC) has exploded in Ijegun, a suburb of Lagos. The incident which happened Thursday morning caused some extensive damage to a number of buildings and cars within the vicinity of the explosion. Already first responders, including fire fighters and security personnel, are already at the scene. More details laterâ€¦
